            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/backlight-cleaner" class="related-slide-card"><img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/backlight-cleaner.jpg" alt="Backlight Panel Cleaning Machine" /><h4>Backlight Panel Cleaning Machine</h4></a>
            <a href="/products/cleaning-machine/inspection-cleaner" class="related-slide-card"><img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/inspection-cleaner.jpg" alt="Inspection Stage Cleaning Machine (STXT Series)" /><h4>Inspection Stage Cleaning Machine (STXT Series)</h4></a>
